name: AGOQ 23.1
description:
All for time: 

3 rounds of: 
2 x 25-ft dumbbell walking lunge (hang position) 
20 toes-to-bars 

Immediately followed by: 

2 rounds of: 
2 x 25-ft dumbbell walking lunge (rack position) 
15 chest-to-bar pull-ups 

Immediately followed by: 

2 x 25-ft dumbbell walking lunge (overhead position) 
10 bar muscle-ups 

♀ 2 x 35-lb dumbbells 
♂ 2 x 50-lb dumbbells 

Teenagers 16-17, Masters 35-54 

♀ 2 x 35-lb dumbbells 
♂ 2 x 50-lb dumbbells 

Teenagers 14-15, Masters 55+ 

♀ 2 x 20-lb dumbbells 
♂ 2 x 35-lb dumbbells 

Time cap: 20 minutes
